  <source>Seoul National University Hospital</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to find a novel method for placing endobronchial blockers
      without fiberoptic guidance to provide one-lung isolation during anesthesia for thoracic
      surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
